    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主干：Start节点标注为FinTech_PaymentGateway，通过Receive Request箭头连接到CheckAddress判断节点，标注为FinTech_LedgerService。",
